summary: A preset of my dunmer character, Eva.
descriptionHtml:
Wow another dark elf, who would have thought? she was suppoused to be [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81324/?]Ember's[/url] new face (that's why they might look a bit alike), but i ended up making a new character entirely oops. 

Anywayysssss here's the requirements:
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu (duh) [/url]

"Soft" requirements, only needed if you want her to look exactly as in the pics (remember that your graphics setup will also affect the character's looks):
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82446/?]UNPCM HDT[/url]
- [url=http://amiablearcher.tumblr.com/post/82351598993/its-time-once-again-for-a-female-texture-update]Main Body Textures[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin (Makeup only)
[/url]- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82588/?]Improved Eyes[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7403/?]Lovely Hairstyles CE[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72825/?]Maevan2's Eyebrows[/url]

Recommended (but not required):
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54416/?]Eye Normal Map Fix 
- [/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7127/?]RAN's Headmesh Variants (Type C)[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13457/?]Facelight[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/84714/?]Better Lightning for Facelight[/url]

Possible Issues:
-There's a neckseam that's noticeable from certain angles, i don't know how to fix this so it's gonna stay like that for now. I don't even know if it's related to the preset because all the females in my game have it lmao

-Her ears are a bit asymmetrical i think? ???

Also check out my other presets if you wish:
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81315/?]Agnetha (Breton)[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81324/?]Ember (Dunmer)[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82684/?]Basthet (Dunmer)[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86526/?]- [/url][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86762?]Elon - Bosmer[/url]
